{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-12527/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-12527"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["1:25:27"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["full shot"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["low"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["fixed"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["two shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["Woman closes door and looks behind her at other woman"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-12527/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-12527","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-12527/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-12527"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-12527/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-12527/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-12527/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-12527/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-12527/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-12527/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-12527/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-12527/canvas/1/06dd573f-91ba-43c6-9dcb-f75aae95f173","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T17:52:42.401Z","creator":"lucia","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Despite the coded tiff they have just had in front of Dr. Hardy, Alma and Cyril don’t address the tension between them. So much is communicated in the silences and glares between characters in <em>Phantom Thread</em>.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-12527/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:681.8181818181819,263.37662337662334,388.83116883116884,720"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-12527/canvas/1/16e0e7a1-2da6-4a21-bd6f-2efc5f7ed6dc","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T17:53:45.784Z","creator":"lucia","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>The metal bars of the stairs that appear in front of the camera lend the shot a sense of imprisonment, though which character is imprisoned remains somewhat unclear. Perhaps it is Reynolds, left upstairs, completely helpless with his illness. Or perhaps it is Alma and Cyril, who seem unable, or unwilling, to disentangle themselves from his life. They stand between the bars and the door, and while both women could walk outside the house, neither choose to. Or maybe it is all three of them, trapped in their triangulation, and the women’s battle over who will be the foremost female figure in Reynolds’ life.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-12527/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:84.15584415584416,99.74025974026009,1726.753246753247,836.8831168831169"}}}]}]}]}